{"tid":1088695,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角衝突再3人被控參與暴動刑毁縱火","createTime":"2019-04-02T08:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T05:22:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c69c4519fadc0f2c401f5b1837b74e0f7089285","tid":1088695,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"2016年農曆年初二旺角大衝突，再有3人分別被控參與暴動、刑事毁壞及縱火，案件今日在區域法院提堂。辯方需時索取法律意見，申請押後，法官准許並將案件押後至5月16日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n3名男被告依次為報稱酒保的譚百熙（21歲）、報稱游泳教練的陳舜堯（30歲）、報稱學生的王國斌（22歲）。譚被控一項暴動罪，指他在2016年2月9日在旺角豉油街，連同其他人參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n譚和王共同被控一項刑事毁壞罪，指兩人於上述日子在山東街，連同其他人在無合理辯解而損壞該處屬於特區政府的財產，即一塊指示牌。王另被控一項刑事毁壞罪，指他於同日在山東街損壞行人路。陳舜堯則被控一項縱火罪，指他於上述日子，在無合理辯解下用火損壞屬中國香港體操總會的一幅橫額。"},{"pid":"bd6727d374efd783d64cbace8ae22283de543f32","tid":1088695,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33febc2e0a4426e29c9f6917bb70e30e6f4e89f","tid":1088695,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e261690f98f990a203686f2a36edd2061d479de9","tid":1088695,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"2047先告呀"},{"pid":"2c27cfcd4f2dc9cd908922bc4f29ee6567c9b12c","tid":1088695,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"告咗鄭若驊僭建未?"},{"pid":"ef575317cb540853e22ded0c83a3b57adb8aa76d","tid":1088695,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"DKLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adcfd0849490b669275f6a54d2bb588894fcedd","tid":1088695,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply